00:13:18.562 --> 00:13:22.152
passengers detected surprisingly little, apparently.

00:13:22.682 --> 00:13:27.132
There was the initial burst of speed when the plane took off — but

00:13:27.372 --> 00:13:32.552
once they reached cruising altitude, the flight was as smooth as glass.

