00:14:20.322 --> 00:14:25.145
Considering the fact that most of the people subjected to this racket,

00:14:25.225 --> 00:14:29.985
to this loud noise, were those who would never be able to afford

00:14:30.195 --> 00:14:34.408
to fly on the Concorde, it was a bit like adding insult to injury.

