00:17:42.879 --> 00:17:48.649
a cruise ship bound for South America, it was to be the trip of a lifetime.

00:17:50.219 --> 00:17:53.839
That flight, of course, never made it to JFK.

00:17:54.969 --> 00:17:59.899
